transcript: Would I were. Madness were easy to bear compared with truth like this. Oh my friend, why think you did I go so far around? Why take so long to tell so simple a thing? Was it because I hate you and have hated you all my life? Was it because I wish to give you pain? Was it because I wanted to give you, now so late, revenge for that time you saved my life, and from a fearful death. Ah no.
title: David
